{"tid":1394123,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"夢遊look","createTime":"2019-08-01T10:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T10:20:34.000Z","uid":279852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"655ce248fc6f75243c93181c9928c1090d984705","tid":1394123,"uid":279852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:04:58.000Z","msg":"有個post講到夢遊前後要換衫。<br />\n<br />\n唔只換衫，其實可以轉look, 舉兩個例：<br />\n<br />\n1 踩板look, 去踩板梗系要戴頭盔護膝。而且塊板咁硬，改裝下可以用黎做盾。<br />\n<br />\n2 自由行look, 著到大陸水客咁，拉住個喼。咁個喼可以放好多物資。<br />\n<br />\n出發夢遊時用上面呢D look，再搵地方換衫。"},{"pid":"191218c36f051a8b16931ee676a7a4d8249f9bd0","tid":1394123,"uid":279852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:20:34.000Z","msg":"光復香港"}]}